## 🧠 The 5 OpenClaw Agentic Skills
Rather than a monolith, the agent's brain is separated into 5 independent executable scripts adhering to OpenClaw standards. Each runs as a distinct Node process.

| Skill | Cost / Protocol | Action / Description |
|-------|-----------------|----------------------|
| `/stellar-wallet` | Free | Queries Horizon for exact Agent and Provider USDC/XLM balances. |
| `/stellar-poll-price` | `$0.01` (MPP SDK) | Fetches the current price matrix. Intercepts HTTP 402 and auto-signs Soroban transaction via `mppx/client`. |
| `/stellar-analyze` | Free | In-memory calculation evaluating momentum, trend, and volume. Calculates a 0-100% "Confluence Score". |
| `/stellar-x402-intel` | `$0.05` (x402 SDK) | Hits premium endpoint. Responds to base64 payment challenge via `@x402/fetch` and settles via `x402.org/facilitator`. |
| `/stellar-trade` | Network Gas | Executes limit orders on the SDEX and calculates P&L. Writes AI reasoning to on-chain memo. |

