## 🛡️ Risk Management Engine
The agent will never run out of control. It executes safe M2M commerce bounded by strict constraints:
1. **Budget Cap**: Agent halts all intel/price polling if the 1.00 USDC micro-payment budget is exhausted.
2. **Max Drawdown**: SDEX Trading is physically halted if cumulative P&L exceeds -15%.
3. **Hard Cooldown**: Minimum 60-second delay between executed trades to prevent wash trading and gas bleeding.
4. **Position Limits**: The agent calculates max exposure and will not risk 100% of portfolio health on a single trade.

