## 🚀 Quick Start / Setup Instruction

**1. Clone and Install**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/xinnxz/hackathon-stellar.git
cd hackathon-stellar
npm run install:all
```

**2. Fund Wallets & Establish Trustlines**
```bash
npm run setup      # Generates dual keypairs & calls Friendbot
npm run trustline  # Establishes USDC Testnet SAC trustlines
npm run seed       # Seeds initial price history buffer
```

**3. Run the Fleet**
```bash
npm run demo
```
*This `concurrently` command spins up:*
- `[MPP]` Price Server on Port 3002
- `[x402]` Intel Server on Port 3003
- `[API]` Agent Orchestrator on Port 3000
- `[UI]` React Dashboard on Port 5173

**4. Interact**
Open `http://localhost:5173`. Click the **▶ Start** button to unleash the agent. Watch the CLI or dashboard ledger as it autonomously negotiates 402 protocols and settles trades on-chain.
